description: Number of partitions of n into 3 nonnegative cubes.
links: Charles R Greathouse IV, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..10000
prog: (PARI) a(n)=sum(a=0,sqrtnint(n,3), sum(b=0,a, my(C=n-a^3-b^3,c); ispower(C,3,&c) && 0 <= c && c <= b)) \\ _Charles R Greathouse IV_, Jun 26 2013
author: _David W. Wilson_
